                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>canadian8703 wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"> is this true? </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
This is something you will have to decide for yourself. There will be folks here who will tell you "most definately yes" - some of those still play, some don't. Then you have some eternal optimist (such as myself) who still enjoy the game and don't see the issues that enchanters face as life or death, and will tell you that it is all in how you look at it.
<br />

<br />
KT+ in GoD and most of OoW sucks for chanters. DoN seems to be a boon for enchanters. Prior to GoD, only high level raiding was pretty boring for enchanters (although there are a few exceptions).
<br />

<br />
My only advice is to form your own opinion. If you rely on folks here to make up your mind, then you have a 50/50 chance of making the right decision for you where you save yourself heartache or miss out on something great.
<br />

<br />
The hard part is weeding out the extreme opinions (for and against) and diving into the facts that matter to you.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-style: italic">That is all I have to say about that! - Forest Gump</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
