<br />
Learn? Yes for pre-pop. Get use to having? NO.
<br />

<br />
Major DPS? ONLY in pre-PoP zones. In OoW it is crap DPS compared to the risk.
<br />

<br />
In GoD and OoW forget about charming in a group situation. My Animation fully buffed does around half the damage of a charmed pet in those zones and I can buff it and not worry about wiping the group when charm breaks during a pull. A group can chain pull without having to pause every 8 minutes or so to try and get my pet back under control or rez me on a charm resist.
<br />

<br />
The RvR is completely unbalanced for in group charming and the down time spent by groups due to the time wasted having to rez dead Enchanters, mana loss from healers keeping chanters alive, time spent recharming on breaks, and down time due group wipes on bad breaks.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Foreverwise
