                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Foreverwise wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I may be wrong about the nerfage in GoD but I could have swore they had a nerf patch where more MOBs were made uncharmable and some, as it appeared to me, were hitting for less. It's been 6 months since I was in GoD xping so my memory could be faulty and if it is I apologize for the mistatement. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
