</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Also note I personally consider any zone that doesn't have a DC mob for me, that doesn't have charmable MOBs, or where Charmed MOBs are hitting for less then when not charmed a nerfed zone</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
