                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Truthfully, if I could start over from when I first bought EQ with the knowledge I know now, I still would have enchanter high on the pick list.  Enchanter wasn't my first class, or even my third, but it was and is definitly my favorite.  The only class I might have chosen over Enchanter if I repicked would be Bard or.. no well Bard.  They have alot of the things that made an Enchanter fun, more ac/life,  no buffs (hehehe) and are wanted everywhere just about.  I'mnot saying Bards are everything a chanter is and more, (aka why be a chanter) but there is definitly enough overlap that if you like Enchanter, Bard is a good pick (given you can stand twisting).</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
